Additional To: aaday@rccl.com
CC: 
BCC: 
Attachment: Royal Caribbean Cruise Lines.pdf

Subject: Deep Freeze Renewal Quote - Royal Caribbean Cruise Lines
Body:
Hi Aurora,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 10 Deep Freeze licenses has expired on
January 16, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian
Faronics

Additional To: jessica.miles@ckcac.org
CC: 
BCC: 
Attachment: Central Kentucky Community Action (CKCA).pdf

Subject: Deep Freeze Renewal Quote - Central Kentucky Community Action (CKCA)
Body:
Hi Jessica,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 3 Deep Freeze licenses will expire on March
29, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian
Faronics

Hi Lisa,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 17 Deep Freeze licenses has expired on March
1, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian

Hi Dan,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 10 Deep Freeze licenses will expire on March
24, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Body:
Hi Katie,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 16 Deep Freeze licenses will expire on March
16, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian
Faronics
benjamin.sebastian@faronics.com
(800) 943-6422 X 4021

Subject: Deep Freeze Maintenance Renewal
Body:
Hi Chris,

How are you?

I just left you a voicemail about your expired maintenance on 4 Deep Freeze Mac  licenses. Your  Maintenance Agreement actually expired in January.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the the time and money-saving benefits of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug fixes.

I have attached a quote showing options for 3 and 5 years of extended maintenance.  You renewed for 5 years last time.

You will find a convenient credit card authorization form on the 2nd page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't hesitate to call me.

Dennis

Hi carrie,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 6 Deep Freeze licenses will expire on June 3,
2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Subject: Deep Freeze Renewal Quote - Kennebec County
Body:
Hi Jason,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 4 Deep Freeze licenses has expired on
February 17, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 4 Deep Freeze licenses will expire on
February 17, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Additional To: aaron.hanchett@cblegacy.com
CC: 
BCC: 
Attachment: Coldwell Banker Legacy.pdf

Subject: Deep Freeze Renewal Quote - Coldwell Banker Legacy
Body:
Hi Aaron,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 2 Deep Freeze licenses has expired on
February 14, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian
Faronics

Subject: Deep Freeze Renewal Quote - Coldwell Banker Legacy
Body:
Hi Aaron,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 2 Deep Freeze licenses will expire on
February 14, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian
Faronics
benjamin.sebastian@faronics.com
(800) 943-6422 X 4021

Body:
Hi Michael,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 20 Deep Freeze licenses will expire on
November 1, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

page.

hesitate to call me.

Subject: Deep Freeze Renewal Quote - Green Doors
Body:
Hi Elias,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 15 Deep Freeze licenses will expire on March
15, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian
Faronics

Nikita Raguzin

Thank you, we've received it and sent it up to Development. We'll keep you posted with any updates.

Best Regards,

I uploaded the Zipped File

Albert Fang

On Tue, Feb 7, 2023 at 8:46 PM, Nikita Raguzin <support@faronics.com> wrote via Mail:

Hello Albert,

Hope you're doing well, Development has had some time to Review your Data and it appears that we're missing some Data. Could you please re-run the Data Collection tool on the Machine with the Core Server one more time and upload it? If we still do not get the Data collection our developers would like to schedule another remote session with you.

Instructions below: 

 

In the process of troubleshooting your issue, it has become apparent that we need to collect some additional data from your client machine(s) or server(s) to get a better understanding of the issue that you are seeing.

 

To make this process as quick as possible we are asking that you download and run our Data Collection tool linked below;

 

https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/faronics-techsupport-utilities/Download/FaronicsDataCollectionTools.exe

 

The data collection tool will generate a ZIP file in the folder that you run it from. This file will be labeled with the name of the system that you are running it on and the date that the utility was run. I would ask you to upload the file to me at the URL below;

 

https://faronics.digitalpigeon.com/rcv/send

 

When uploading the data please ensure that you include the conversation number for this issue (28752)so that the upload can be quickly referenced back to this ticket. Not including the ticket reference number may result in the data being deleted immediately if we cannot link it to an existing ticket.

 

Our data collection tool will automatically extract and send us information about your system including, but not limited to;

 

·Faronics Product Information. (Configuration data, log files)

·Details on installed products, including product names, version numbers, and locations of files.

·Hardware statistics, including processor, hard disk, and other unique identifiers associated with your hardware. (MSINFO Report)

·Event, Application, and Security logs from the client machines.

·Copies of some Faronics files related to the configuration of your systems.

 

While we intend to only collect information relevant to the issue the nature of collecting data from your system in an automated manner may result in the collection of personally identifiable information.

 

All the information collected during this process will be handled per our Privacy Policy and all stipulations in GDPR Article 28(3) where we (Faronics) are the Data Processor and you are the Data Controller.

 

The data that we collect will only be used for purposes of troubleshooting your issue and will be retained for no more than three months. If there is a legitimate need to retain the data for a longer period our team will contact you to secure permission for us to do so.

 

If you have any concerns regarding this data collection please feel free to let us know or contact our data protection officer via email at dpo@faronics.com.

Best Regards,

Nikita Raguzin




On Fri, Feb 3, 2023 at 5:53 PM, Nikita Raguzin <support@faronics.com> wrote via Mail:

Hello Albert,

We've received your Data Collection, we will update you as soon as we hear anything from Development. Please note, I forgot to mention we uninstalled the Faronics AV during our testing, to re-install it you can do so from the Deep Freeze Console just create a "Work station Seed installer" by going to "Tools" ->Configuration Administrator->"Create" Button -> Create Workstation Seed Installer.

Just run this on the Machine after, it should show up in the Deep Freeze Console work station list inside the Deep Freeze Enterprise Console, you can then right click it and select "Install" for Anti-Virus.

Best Regards,

Nikita Raguzin




On Thu, Feb 2, 2023 at 6:46 PM, Nikita Raguzin <support@faronics.com> wrote via Mail:

Hi Albert,

Great, I'll be giving you a call tomorrow around 9am PST.

Best Regards,

Nikita Raguzin

Sent with Kayako

Subject: Deep Freeze Renewal Quote - University of Washington - College of Built Environments
Body:
Hi Allen,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 10 Deep Freeze licenses has expired on
February 24, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian

*Abby Pakhare*

Subject: Deep Freeze Renewal Quote - Southeast Arkansas Regional Library
Body:
Hi Judy,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 10 Deep Freeze licenses will expire on July
3, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian
Faronics

Subject: Deep Freeze Renewal Quote - FactSet Research Systems Inc.
Body:
Dear Customer,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 20 Deep Freeze licenses will expire on March
20, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian
Faronics

Subject: Deep Freeze Renewal Quote - Bethlehem Public Library
Body:
Hi Laura,

How are you?

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you
that the subscription of your 8 Deep Freeze licenses has expired on
February 25, 2023.

If you plan to continue enjoying all of the time and money-saving benefits
of Deep Freeze, then keeping maintenance current ensures you always have
free access to our latest versions, plus Premium Tech Support, and any bug
fixes.

I have attached a quote for your review and approval.

You will also find a convenient credit card authorization form on the last
page.

If you have any questions at all concerning the quote, please don't
hesitate to call me.

Kindly ignore if already renewed.

Benjamin Sebastian
Faronics

I'm with the renewals team here at Faronics, and I'm writing to remind you

Good morning, you are wanting me to purchase again.
I have a huge problem with your standard deepfreeze.  
I bought a second copy to protect my simulator for user changes and I have to fix things on the sim regularly.
I use PROTON VPN and I set the login before I freeze the system.  When I go to use it looses the login and password.
I load up a plane in sim with parameters and then the plane doesn't remember.
what is going on? I dont care to waste more money having to do the same things as before I had your software.
I use win10, I7, nvidia 2080ti, 2 2tb drives, and 36gb memory.  Maybe this is the problem, I don't know.
--
Terry Haley 575-914-8370
jetfun@gmail.com

I have a huge problem with your standard deepfreeze.  
I bought a second copy to protect my simulator for user changes and I have to fix things on the sim regularly.
I use PROTON VPN and I set the login before I freeze the system.  When I go to use it looses the login and password.
I load up a plane in sim with parameters and then the plane doesn't remember.
what is going on? I dont care to waste more money having to do the same things as before I had your software.
I use win10, I7, nvidia 2080ti, 2 2tb drives, and 36gb memory.  Maybe this is the problem, I don't know.
--
Terry Haley 575-914-8370

Subject: Deep Freeze Maintenance Renewal Quotation
Body:
Hi Steve,

How are you?

This is a quick reminder that the maintenance on your 19 Deep Freeze Licenses is expiring on March 23.

I trust that Deep Freeze is still living up to your expectations?

When you purchased  last year, the maintenance was included as part of that purchase.
This year is your first opportunity to renew your maintenance package, so you may have some questions about the upcoming renewal.

Simply stated, keeping maintenance ​current is essential to achieve the absolute best results you can from the software. Why? Because with current maintenance you are always able to download any upgrades or changes to the software. Plus, you have telephone access to our expert and knowledgeable staff in tech support, and automatically receive any necessary bug fixes. Without maintenance, you have rights only to your current version.  In effect, maintenance protects your investment.

Please review the attached quote, with options for 1 and 3 years of extended maintenance. Note the discount when choosing the 3-year term.

Don't hesitate to let me know if you have any questions, and I look forward to hearing from you.

Regards,

Dennis Winkelmans
Maintenance Renewals Manager
Faronics

Tel: 1-800-943-6422 x (4049 )
Email: dennis@faronics.com
